title: System Roads
name: System Roads
description: This feature class contains roads that are routed and have matching entries in INFRA.  It originally came from the travel_route_road feature class (preceded by the travel_route coverage, route.roads), and is intended to have a one-to-one relationship with INFRA and ideally everything entered in INFRA will also be represented spatially.   SDI was originally used to calibrate the route measures.  GPS files of roads have replaced some of the roads from the original coverage.  This feature class is now the most up-to-date version of roads.
